vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to Bijoy, LLC, for the use of approximately 27 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize a premise blade sign over portions of Main and Harwood Streets rights-of-way located near its intersection with Harwood Street - Revenue: General Fund $1,000.00 annual fee, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
